Zeitgeist plugin to the XChat irc client
****************************************

To use this plugin:

* Install Zeitgeist 0.3 (or greater)
* Type "make" and "sudo make install" for a system-wide installation; "make" and "make local-install"
  for a local installation
  
*************************************************************************************************************
  N.B. Please don't install both system-wide and locally! XChat will load both plugins, getting double events
  on your Zeitgeist.
*************************************************************************************************************
